# Krasny Yar, Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Krasny Yar () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 378 as of 2010. There are 19 streets.
Geography
Krasny Yar is located 54&nbsp;km north of Kabansk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Novaya Derevnya is the nearest rural locality.
